		"description": "Setting 'extendBackground' to _true_ extends the screen not only behind the StatusBar, but also behind the software system navigation buttons on devices with one. \r\n\r\nTest case:\r\n*index.xml*\r\n\r\n{code:xml}\r\n<Alloy>\r\n\t<Window title=\"My Test App\" backgroundColor=\"gray\" customToolbar=\"toolbar\">\r\n\t\t<Toolbar\r\n\t\t\tid=\"toolbar\"\r\n\t\t\ttitle=\"MyMenu\"\r\n\t\t\tsubtitle=\"Subtitle\"\r\n\t\t\twidth=\"Ti.UI.FILL\"\r\n\t\t\ttop=\"0\"\r\n\t\t\tbarColor=\"#639851\"\r\n\t\t\textendBackground= \"true\"/>\r\n\t</Window>\r\n</Alloy>\r\n{code}\r\n",
